{"tid":1703602,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家提醒所有市民，唔好畀暴徒用以下方式影響鐵路運作","createTime":"2019-11-10T10:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T11:43:00.000Z","uid":42751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93277eb8f7671d1a06ff353219f74cca911365f8","tid":1703602,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"大家聽日千祈唔好跌咗把遮入西鐵路軌， 然後再叫職員落路軌執番， 咁樣會阻止到西鐵運作，影響大家返工<br />\n<br />\n因為任何金屬物件跌入路軌都必須要立即清理，<br />\n所以大家千祈唔好唔小心跌咗遮、士巴拿、螺絲批等等金屬物件入路軌範圍<br />\n<br />\n如果你坐西鐵由屯門坐到去紅磡， 千祈唔好俾人每個站都跌一把遮落去， 咁樣嘅話一把遮就可以搞到每個暫停幾分鐘<br />\n<br />\n祝願大家聽日可以準時返工，為香港經濟作出貢獻， 一定要阻止嗰啲破壞社會安寧嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15dd6024f103ce699b53a2f30a842df511e0ab14","tid":1703602,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbdd1ed0a6bce8919c706fc8d718f61b8576278","tid":1703602,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad13d1b74cc9e8fe35c8e037d33912ce2c542e6b","tid":1703602,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}